<raw><![CDATA[ BRUSSELS, March 15 (Reuters) - The European Commission isready to propose to euro zone finance ministers a mechanism thatcould be used for financial assistance for Greece, Economic andMonetary Affairs Commissioner Olli Rehn said on Monday. "The Commission is ready to table a proposal for a Europeanframework for coordinated and conditional assistance," Rehn toldreporters ahead of the meeting of euro zone ministers, theEurogroup.(Reporting by Marcin Grajewski, writing by Jan Strupczewski,editing by Patrick Graham)              ]]></raw>
